”’Щ@3588eebe6433bd4093ea599b097b03f065dbcd3b8cc30c419291da9cd3fddd8dЪ	mTitle: This week in Nushell #208
Path: Nushell
Content:
fdncred 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10048] allowed ints as a cellpath for 
``select``
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9987] allowed 
``select``
 to take a $variable with a list of columns
kubouch 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10040] removed dead code from tests
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10039] sorted entries in 
``scope``
 commands; Fix usage of externs
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10038] changed 
``str replace``
 to match substring by default
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10023] refactored 
``scope``
 commands
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10004] fixed example for 
``extern-wrapped``
sitiom 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10032] changed the winget releaser job to 
``ubuntu-latest``
ineu 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10022] made 
``http -f``
 display the request headers
amtoine created 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10017] deprecate 
``--format``
 and 
``--list``
 in 
``into datetime``
ayax79 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10019] exposed polars avro support
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9951] Nushell table list columns -> dataframe list columns. Explode / Flatten dataframe support.
3lvir4 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10012] removed a potential panic from path join
zhiburt 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10011] fixed padding 0 width issues in nu-table
meskill 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10007] fixed nu-parser to not update plugin.nu file on nu startup
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9976] test: clear parent envs to prevent leakage to tests
sholderbach 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/10000] renamed misused "deprecation" to removal
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9998] improved I/O types of 
``into decimal``
(/float)
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9996] Add search terms to 
``reject``
rgwood 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9990] fixed 
``watch``
 not handling all file changes
nibon7 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/9784] fixed a crash when moving the cursor after accepting a suggestion from the help menu
